headline: AvalonBay Communities, Inc. Announces First Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Date
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., April 03, 2025--AVALONBAY COMMUNITIES, INC. (NYSE: AVB) (the "Company") will release its first quarter 2025 earnings on April 30, 2025 after the market close. The Company will hold a conference call on May 1, 2025 at 1:00 PM Eastern Time (ET) to discuss its first quarter 2025 results.
